channel.title: Offering help with programming
channel.description:
I'm doing an education which has a part of java programming. Now I'd like to practice my java programming and thought someone here might need my help.
I'm not new to programming private servers of runescape, I did it a few years back and was having my own private server. It was actually a success but I was running on a crap pc and then it's no wonder that i had lots of lag.
I'm searching for someone which already has a server running because I won't help with hamachi or no-ip crap. I'm willing to code difficult things, but not things like placing a thousand npc's which is very easy and just a lot of work.
I've posted before and it got locked. Maybe because I was confused with someone who wants to steal files... To clear that up, I don't need any of your private server files. But it would be useful to know what source u used.
So... again, anyone interested?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: January 29, 2009, 04:59:38 am[/size][hr]ah, shiit.. moving to the right section, sorry, lock it :rolleyes:
